{"tid":1043010,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［求戲名］一個任性女孩為滿足自己貪玩好奇心而放棄初戀","createTime":"2019-03-02T02:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T06:01:52.000Z","uid":5247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d1fec76eecf2db64763d09d98cadd68d6ce962","tid":1043010,"uid":5247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"我諗套戲應該都有6/7年前,係歐美電影嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事大概講一個女仔同佢男朋友係大學拍拖,畢業個陣個女仔話一直同個男仔拍拖冇乜經歷過其他事,好似浪費緊自己青春咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要同個男仔分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後去第二到發展。<br />\n<br />\n跟住故事內容都係講女主角去到新地方,因為初初接觸花花世界,所以日蒲夜蒲。最後踏上公廁之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好到最後當佢發現身邊每個男人都係為同佢上床之後,就開始後悔當初離開自己初戀,於是想翻撻重新嚟過並搵翻初戀男友埋單,但最後失敗左。<br />\n<br />\n最後係講個女仔開始接受單身既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999,但我已經盡力還原翻個故事內容出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0148bdded40fc63a29fae0a882c907486f49c340","tid":1043010,"uid":33878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"六弄咖啡館"},{"pid":"fa12ba733410404db696a93b3e70349ee0b61439","tid":1043010,"uid":8345,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97fa2509c2f7857a937bcf0b4f4e377fbb480164","tid":1043010,"uid":5247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0148bdded40fc63a29fae0a882c907486f49c340","tid":1043010,"uid":33878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"六弄咖啡館"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"我記得係外國電影嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acea646142967045e4f4085aed13249312a3b55","tid":1043010,"uid":5247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid"